Global setup:
 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email basjargsu@gmail.com
        
Next steps:
  mkdir gallerysite
  cd gallerysite
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:basjargsu/site2.git
  git push origin master

To merge:

git checkout -b annaship-master master

git pull https://github.com/annaship/site2.git master

git checkout master
git merge annaship-master
git push origin master